channel.description:
[CENTER][img]http://i.imgur.com/137FsfO.gif[/img]
[SIZE=3][URL=http://"http://entranapk.com/"]Index[/URL] - [URL=http://"http://forum.entranapk.com/"]Forums[/URL] - [URL=http://"http://entranapk.com/play"]Play now[/URL][/SIZE]
[b][SIZE=2] Entrana PK is a 24/7 spawn PK server which offers the best PK'ing experience out there with good, structured economy. We at Entrana realize that some people prefer oldschool data and some newschool, that's why we provide numerous of settings, such as Oldschool mode, 525 mode (mid 2008), and 667 (new school). You'll be able to switch between settings like gameframes, new or old hitpoints bar, x10 health and x10 prayer.
Entrana gives you the best and quickest hybridding or any other kind of PK'ing. With a quick and simple interface which allows you to create custom PK sets. These PK sets include spell book changing, prayer changing, level changing, inventory and equipment changing. With a one tap of a buttom you will be ready to fight.To make clanning even easier this interface can generate copy code so others can enjoy sets you have created.
We have an outstanding achievements system, whether it's PK'ing achievements or PvM achievements, you'll love them. The achievements give you great rewards such as PvP armour and even Chaotics.
We have a really unique Summoning system which gets as real to RuneScape as it gets. We have perfect special attacks, summoning familiars run, familiar inventory and so on. So grab your summoning pouches if that's your thing.
Enjoy our Player Vs Monster fighting to the maximum, take on the corporeal beast, tormented demons or even the king black dragon.
